	Tea tree essential oil is nature&rsquo;s antiseptic, anti-fungal&nbsp;and all round healing oil. This cream has a wide range of uses and is one of those items that you should always have in the house, first aid box and take on holiday. Great for use on athletes foot and nail infections plus spots, boils, burns, corns, itching (from insect bites, chicken pox, etc) warts, cold sores, scratches or grazes etc. Tea tree has been successfully used on nail infections and athletes foot for years now and we supply ours to local chiropodists. This is a ready to apply cream and to use simply apply to the affected area and rub in. For use on feet massage the ointment into clean feet and toes twice daily.</p>
